DateTime::Locale::bas(3) User Contributed Perl Documentation DateTime::Locale::bas(3)

NAME

DateTime::Locale::bas - Locale data examples for the Basaa (bas) locale

DESCRIPTION

This pod file contains examples of the locale data available for the Basaa locale.

Days

  ŋgwà njaŋgumba
  ŋgwà ûm
  ŋgwà ŋgê
  ŋgwà mbɔk
  ŋgwà kɔɔ
  ŋgwà jôn
  ŋgwà nɔ̂y

  uum
  ŋge
  mbɔ
  kɔɔ
  jon
  nɔy

Wide (format)

  bisū bi Yesù Krǐstò
  i mbūs Yesù Krǐstò

  m.Y.K

  b.Y.K
  m.Y.K

Date Formats

Full

   2008-02-05T18:30:30 = ŋgwà ûm 5 Màcɛ̂l 2008
   1995-12-22T09:05:02 = ŋgwà kɔɔ 22 Lìbuy li ńyèe 1995
  -0010-09-15T04:44:23 = ŋgwà jôn 15 Dìpɔ̀s -10

Long

   2008-02-05T18:30:30 = 5 Màcɛ̂l 2008
   1995-12-22T09:05:02 = 22 Lìbuy li ńyèe 1995
  -0010-09-15T04:44:23 = 15 Dìpɔ̀s -10

Medium

   2008-02-05T18:30:30 = 5 mac, 2008
   1995-12-22T09:05:02 = 22 liɓ, 1995
  -0010-09-15T04:44:23 = 15 dip, -10

Short

   2008-02-05T18:30:30 = 5/2/2008
   1995-12-22T09:05:02 = 22/12/1995
  -0010-09-15T04:44:23 = 15/9/-10

Datetime Formats

  -0010-09-15T04:44:23 = ŋgwà jôn 15 Dìpɔ̀s -10 04:44:23 UTC

   2008-02-05T18:30:30 = 5 Màcɛ̂l 2008 18:30:30 UTC

Available Formats

Bh (h B)

   1995-12-22T09:05:02 = 9 B
  -0010-09-15T04:44:23 = 4 B
